\par \pard\plain \s66\sa120\sl281\slmult1 \f5\fs20 Click the Add push button on the Index dialog to Add an index file other than the table's structural compound index file.  ProMatrix displays the Open dialog.
\par \pard\plain \s67\sl281\slmult1 \f5\fs20 
Use the Open dialog to find the index file you wish to Add.  When you've found the index file you want, click the Open button.  ProMatrix displays the file in the Index dialog list box.  While the index file is displayed and highlighted in the list box, y
ou can use the Modify, Reindex and Delete buttons with it.
