\par \pard\plain \s66\sa120\sl281\slmult1 \f5\fs20 Highlight an index in the list box and click the Modify push button on the Index dialog to modify the index.  ProMatrix displays the Create/Modify Index dialog.
\par \pard\plain \s67\sl281\slmult1 \f5\fs20 Use this dialog to modify the index expression or index Options.  You may not modify the File path and name or the Tag name.
