To identify a field name change on the Data Dictionary Update dialog
\par \pard\plain \s17\fi-360\li360\sb120\sl281\slmult1\tx360 \f5\fs20 {\*\bkmkstart D2HBulletNumber21}1.\tab Highlight the new field name in the table fields list in the list box.
