\par {\f1 \'b7\tab }{\b Field Labels:}  Enter a label for each field that will be on a screen or report.
\par {\f1 \'b7\tab }{\b F{\*\bkmkend D2HBulletNumber26}ield Pictures:}  Enter a picture for each field that will be on a screen or report.
