\par \pard\plain \s16\sb120\sl281\slmult1 \f5\fs20 
When you click the Integrity check box, ProMatrix displays the Integrity dialog.  You use the Integrity dialog to set up the validation rules for a field. Your selections and entries on the Integrity dialog determine how a field is validated when it is ed
ited on a screen.
\par The Integrity check box displays a check after you set up validation for a field on the Integrity dialog.
