\par \pard\plain \s16\sb120\sl281\slmult1 \f5\fs20 You check the Unique check box to prevent duplicate entries into a field on a screen you build in ProMatrix.
\par \pard \s16\sb120\sl281\slmult1\brdrt\brdrs\brdrw15\brsp20 \brdrb\brdrs\brdrw15\brsp20 {\b 
