\par \pard\plain \s16\sb120\sl281\slmult1 \f5\fs20 Click the Picture check box to enter a picture expression for a field.  ProMatrix displays the Picture dialog.  Enter the field's picture expression in the Picture field on the dialog.
\par When you create a screen or report for a table, ProMatrix automatically inserts the field picture expressions.  If you later change a field's picture expression, run the table Update option to update the screens and reports that display the field.
\par If you need help with picture expressions, refer to the FoxPro {\i Language Reference} manual.
