When a user of your application edits a field that uses Referential validation, pressing F2 or clicking the right mouse button displays a picklist of the valid entries for the field.  The valid entries are the primary key v
alues in the Reference table.  The user can select a value for the field from the picklist by double-clicking a value in the list or by highlighting a value and pressing enter.
