 SECTION1:0260}}{\f103  }Editing the F2 Help Picklist Browse
\par \pard\plain \s66\sa120\sl281\slmult1 \f5\fs20 When a user clicks the Edit button on an F2 Help picklist, an edit window replaces the picklist.  All the fields in the currently selected record in the Reference table are displayed vertically in edit mode.

