\pard\plain \s83 \b\f5\fs20 {\cs82\fs16\up6 +} SECTION1:0265}}{\f103  }F2 Help Picklist Not Available for Browse Screens
\par \pard\plain \s16\sb120\sl281\slmult1 \f5\fs20 
The F2 Help picklist is not available for fields that use Referential validation when the field is edited on a ProMatrix Browse screen.  The F2 Help picklist is itself a Browse window, and it is not possible to activate it from a ProMatrix Browse screen.

