\par \pard\plain \s16\sb120\sl281\slmult1 \f5\fs20 ProMatrix includes the following two data dictionary reports in the applications it creates:
\par \pard\plain \s62\fi-360\li360\sb120\sl281\slmult1\tx360 \f5\fs20 {\f1 {\*\bkmkstart D2HBulletNumber62}\'b7\tab }{\b Data Dictionary Report} - lists the tables and fields in an application's data dictionary;  shows important field properties.
\par {\f1 \'b7\tab }{\b T{\*\bkmkend D2HBulletNumber62}able Relations Report} - shows how tables are related in an application;  relations are based on Referential validation setup.
