\par \pard\plain \s66\sa120\sl281\slmult1 \f5\fs20 When you want to create a new report or label for an application, begin by clicking the New button on the Report Manager.  ProMatrix displays the New Report / Label dialog.
\par \pard\plain \s67\sl281\slmult1 \f5\fs20 Enter the file name of the report or label you want to create (up to eight characters).  Click the Report or Label radio button to indicate which you're creating.  Click OK.  The new report name is
 displayed and highlighted on the Report Manager.
\par \pard\plain \s16\sb120\sl281\slmult1 \f5\fs20 After you've named the report, you click the Open button to access the ProMatrix Report Editor to create your report.
