\par \tab Click the New button to begin creating a new user function.  ProMatrix displays the New User Function dialog.  Enter a file name for the function.  Click OK.  The function name appears in the User Functions list.
\par {\f1 \'b7\tab }{\cs71\b Edit}
\par \tab When you want to edit a User Function, highlight it and click the Edit button.  The first time you edit a new function ProMatrix displays the Build Object dialog.
