\par \pard\plain \s17\fi-360\li360\sb120\sl281\slmult1\tx360 \f5\fs20 {\*\bkmkstart D2HBulletNumber70}1.\tab Open the Report Builder/Manager and highlight the report on the report list.  Click Open.  ProMatrix displays the Report Editor.
\par 2.\tab Click the Try It or the Run button, whichever appears on the Report Editor.  ProMatrix displays the Report Setup dialog unless you've chosen not to use the Report Setup dialog on the Options dialog.
\par 3.\tab R{\*\bkmkend D2HBulletNumber70}un the report from the Report Setup dialog after you've set up the run options you want.
\par \pard\plain \s65\sb120 \b\f5\fs20 To run a report from a menu option or as a called object
\par \pard\plain \s76\fi-360\li360\sb120\sl281\slmult1\tx360 \f5\fs20 1.\tab Select the menu option or the control you've created to run the report as a called object.  ProMatrix displays the Report Setup dialog unless you've chosen not to use it.
\par 2.\tab Run the report from the Report Setup dialog after you've set up the run options you want.
