New Password
\par \pard\plain \s66\sa120\sl281\slmult1 \f5\fs20 The New Password dialog requires you to enter a new password that conforms to the rules entered on the Security Setup screen.  
\par \pard\plain \s67\sl281\slmult1 \f5\fs20 
After you enter a valid password, you must enter it again to confirm your entry.  This is necessary because the entries are hidden from view and you may have entered something other than what you had intended.  If you decide to not enter a new password, p
ressing the escape key or the Cancel push button will exit ProMatrix.
\par \pard\plain \s3\sb340\keepn \b\f5\fs28 {\f103 \page }{\cs82\f103\fs16\up6 #{\footnote \pard\plain \s83 \b\f5\fs20 {\cs82\fs16\up6 #} UserData.87}}{\f103\fs24  }{\cs82\f103\fs16\up6 ${\footnote \pard\plain \s83 \b\f5\fs20 {\cs82\fs16\up6 $} User Data}}{
