 Menu Permission Groups Screen}}{\f103  }{\cs82\f103\fs16\up6 K{\footnote \pard\plain \s83 \b\f5\fs20 {\cs82\fs16\up6 K} Menu Permission Groups Screen}}{\f103  }{\cs82\f103\fs16\up6 +{\footnote \pard\plain \s83 \b\f5\fs20 {\cs82\fs16\up6 +} SECTION3:0045}
}{\f103  }Menu Permission Groups Screen
\par \pard\plain \s16\sb120\sl281\slmult1 \f5\fs20 
If a number of users will have the same permissions, you can create a menu permissions group and assign permissions to the group.  Then, users can simply be assigned to this group instead of having to assign permissions to each user individually.
