\par {\f1 \'b7\tab }{\b All Users:}  If you've implemented System Access Security in your application, you can view data changes for all users who have run the application by clicking the All Users radio button in the Filter box.
\par {\f1 \'b7\tab }{\b All Apps:}  If the application is sharing its audit trail file with another application, you can view data changes for all applications by clicking the All Apps radio button in the Filter box.
\par {\f1 \'b7\tab }{\b S{\*\bkmkend D2HBulletNumber131}creen Controls:}  You cannot edit or add audit trail records but you can delete them.  You should delete the audit trail records before you package your application. 
