\par \pard\plain \s16\sb120\sl281\slmult1 \f5\fs20 ProMatrix screens that display single record tables have Edit and OK control buttons.  To update the data on a single record screen, click the Edit button.  
\par The purpose of the Edit mode on these screens is to allow more than one user to access the same screen at the same time.  Some FoxPro applications bring up single record screens in e
